  * new command svwait to wait for supervise service to come up
  * svctool: make inlookup,pwdlookup service wait for 30 seconds since MySQL services comes up
  * svctool: replace /bin/false with /usr/bin/false on FreeBSD
  * sys-checpwd.c: restore '@' sign in username for authmodules in the chain
  * sys-checkpwd.c: skip stripping of domain if STRIP_DOMAIN env variable is not set
  * Makefile: fix perl path in perl scripts
  * removed unused programs - qmail-lagcheck, qmail-lint, elq, pinq, qail
  * added debug statments in sys-checkpwd
  * svctool: added all available authmodules as IMAPMODULES
  * syncdir.c, syncdir.h, qmail-local.c, qmail-queue.c, qmail-send.c, qmail-todo.c: Darwin port for syncdir
  * removed ldap-checkpwd for Darwin. Added it to Linux, FreeBSD Makefile target
  * installer.c: set permissions for directory only if it is a new directory
  * install indimail.plist in shareddir/boot
  * svctool: updated macOSuseradd, macOSgroupadd
  * svctool, svwait: fix date command syntax for Darwin, FreeBSD
  * svctool: --fixedharedlibs for Darwin
